title: [FSX/P3D] Ants Airplanes T-28 Trojan - Complete Package
description:
This is the complete package of Ant's Airplanes T-28 Trojan for you guys and includes the following:

- Ant's T-28A v1.0
- Ant's T-28B&C v1.11
- Ant's T-28D v2.1 (NEW!)
- Ant's T-28 Weapons v1.1

The weapons package is already pre-integrated into the aircraft packages, you do NOT need to install it unless you want to restore the weapons after deleting one of the aircraft packages.

I know T-28A is donationware and T-28B&C has already been shared by me; these new installers are provided to you only to bring them in line with the new T-28D v2.1 installer. If you don't want them, simply don't download & install them!

To prevent the possibility of double shortcuts, delete the old Ant's Airplanes T-28 shortcuts from your Start menu BEFORE beginning the installation and proceed with the installation as instructed in the information pages of the installers.

This package was complete & up-to-date at the time I uploaded this at TPB.

Anthony offers great planes at reasonable prices, support him whenever you can.

SEED & ENJOY!
